objects.name: Welcome to a mysterious forest! You might want to make your way back to your tent
Ooh, Nuts. Grab those and two other ingredients to make a Magic Trail Mix
Press F to eat your Magic Mix. This one teleports you to where you ate it when you press D!
The Magic Mix here will let you walk on clouds. But you might need a way out of this pit... (You can reset from the menu button at the top)
